          "rdfs:label": "Heat Pipe",
          "m0triz:problem": "Transfer heat efficiently across distance without moving parts or external power",
          "m0triz:solution": "Sealed tube with working fluid. Heat causes evaporation at hot end, vapor condenses at cold end releasing heat, liquid returns via capillary action. Phase transition cycle, preliminary action (fluid pre-loaded), universality (passive cooling/heating).",
